name: What'syourfavoritefood
0:
”Alexa, open My Favorite Food.”
”What's my favorite food?”
”Tell me my favorite food.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my favorite food
des: Alexa is good at remembering things - especially food. Tell Alexa what your favorite food is and she'll repeat it back to you when asked!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
